 one who after namaz’e Juma writes AL-HAFEE-ZO 988 times in small writing and tie it on arm will be safe from the whisper of shaitan, fear of kings, wild animals, snake, scorpion and evil thought.", "GujaratiDescription": null, "RUrduDescription": "Hazrat Imam Reza (a) se manqool hai keh roz’e Juma baad az namaz baarik khat (small writing) se 988 martaba AL-HAFEE-ZO likh kar apne baazoo (arm) par bandh lene waala shakhs shaitaan ke waswase, salaatin (baadshaaho’n) ke khouf, darindo’n, saanp, bichchhoo aur khayaalaat’e faasidah (burey khayaalaat) se amaan mein rehta hai.", "UrduDescription": "حضرت امام رضاؑ سے منقول ہے کہ روزِ جمعہ بعد از نماز باریک خط سے 988 مرتبہ ’’اَلْحَفِیْظُ‘‘ لکھ کر اپنے بازو پر باندھ لینے والا شخص وسوسہ شیطانی، سلاطین کے خوف، درندوں، سانپ، بچھو اورخیالات فاسدہ سے امان میں رہتا ہے۔", "English": null, "Gujarati": null, "RGujarati": null, "RUrdu": null, "Urdu": null, "RArabic": null, "ArabicText1": null, "ArabicGreenSign1": null, "ArabicRedSign1": null, "ArabicBlueSign1": null, "ArabicText2": null, "ArabicGreenSign2": null, "ArabicRedSign2": null, "ArabicBlueSign2": null, "ArabicText3": null, "ArabicGreenSign3": null, "ArabicRedSign3": null, "ArabicBlueSign3": null, "ArabicText4": null, "ArabicGreenSign4": null, "ArabicRedSign4": null, "ArabicBlueSign4": null, "ArabicText5": null, "ArabicGreenSign5": null, "ArabicRedSign5": null, "ArabicBlueSign5": null, "ArabicText6": null, "ArabicGreenSign6": null, "ArabicRedSign6": null, "ArabicBlueSign6": null, "ArabicText7": null, "ArabicGreenSign7": null, "ArabicRedSign7": null, "ArabicBlueSign7": null, "ArabicText8": null, "ArabicGreenSign8": null, "ArabicRedSign8": null, "ArabicBlueSign8": null, "ArabicText9": null, "ArabicGreenSign9": null, "ArabicRedSign9": null, "ArabicBlueSign9": null, "ArabicText10": null, "ArabicGreenSign10": null, "ArabicRedSign10": null, "ArabicBlueSign10": null, "ArabicText11": null, "ArabicGreenSign11": null, "ArabicRedSign11": null, "ArabicBlueSign11": null, "ArabicText12": nul